title: PT 3: She Wants Her BFF And Brother To Date But He's About To Propose! + Why Men Choose To Be A Gynecologist
description:
Have you ever wondered when men choose to become gynecologists? We have, and today we have answers!  
But first, remember our listener, Clare? Her brother was about to propose to his girlfriend, but she thought it was going to be a mistake. She knew that her brother and her friend were a better pair. So she reached out to us for help trying to hook them up.
What has happened since we last spoke to her? We have an update!
